Suggested commands:


    snakk extract <file> [ -o <output-file> ]

Extracts the body of the message file.


    snakk header <file> [ -o <output-file> ] [ -f bash | --format=bash ]

Extracts the header of the message file, optionally in a format
accessible to bash scripts.


    snakk envelope <file> [ -o <output-file> ] [ -i <header-file> ]

Prepends headers to the file.